## World-class Innovation

Innovation is at the heart of our business. True to our pioneering spirit, our in-house R&D team works collaboratively with experts worldwide to develop efficacious products, new packaging, sustainable solutions, and new methods to enhance the profiles of our range of products to meet rapid changes in consumer demands and emerging trends. Combining specialised expertise with cutting-edge technologies, every product is formulated with 100% safe and effective science-backed ingredients for proven quality and efficacy.

Our quest for innovation doesn’t just stop here. To optimise our production, we invest in robotic automation & state-of-the-art machinery to integrate our manufacturing processes to maximise efficiency & speed. With our robust R&D & production capabilities, we are always one step ahead.

## Promise Of Quality And Safety

We do not compromise product quality and safety for speed or profit. Our signature wet wipes and solutions are produced with high precision wet wipes production system and advanced bottling system, in our own sophisticated dust-free 100K Clean Room, ISO 9001 certified and GMP Compliant manufacturing facility, under exacting hygiene standards. All products are rigorously tested by reputable laboratories and undergo stringent quality control to meet and surpass international standards.

With manufacturing facilities in Singapore, Indonesia and China, certification of Business Continuity Management and a $2M Product Liability Insurance, we go above and beyond to ensure that our clients and stakeholders are protected in the event of unexpected situations are able to assure ongoing, uninterrupted supply.

