### ISO 9001

An internationally recognised Quality Management System (QMS) standard for organisations to demonstrate the ability to consistently provide products and services that meet customer and regulatory requirements.

![](https://freshening.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/image-119-2.png)

### ISO 13485

A quality management system standard specifically for the medical devices industry, where an organization needs to demonstrate its ability to provide medical devices and related services that consistently meet customer and regulatory requirements.

![](https://freshening.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/FSC-1.png)

### FSC Certified (C152695)

Selected products meet the requirements of Forest Stewardship Council - An international, non-governmental organisation dedicated to promoting responsible management of the world’s forests. Materials used in these wipes are from FSC-certified forests, recycled materials, and/or FSC-controlled wood.

![](https://freshening.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/fddd6968741e6bbfa0877c7e6ba664c.png)

### Halal Certified

Our alcohol-free wipes and napkins is compliant with Halal requirements, meeting the guidelines for purity and hygiene.